{"id":6502,"date":"2023-09-27T04:41:28","date_gmt":"2023-09-27T04:41:28","guid":{"rendered":"http:\/\/roperbenefits.info\/medicare-help\/"},"modified":"2023-09-29T04:28:14","modified_gmt":"2023-09-29T04:28:14","slug":"medicare-help","status":"publish","type":"page","link":"https:\/\/roperbenefits.info\/2024-benefits\/medicare-help\/","title":{"rendered":"Medicare Help"},"content":{"rendered":"\t\t<div data-elementor-type=\"wp-page\" data-elementor-id=\"6502\" class=\"elementor elementor-6502\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<section class=\"elementor-section elementor-top-section elementor-element elementor-element-fe6e8d1 elementor-section-boxed elementor-section-height-default elementor-section-height-default\" data-id=\"fe6e8d1\" data-element_type=\"section\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-container elementor-column-gap-default\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-column elementor-col-100 elementor-top-column elementor-element elementor-element-bc1aeff\" data-id=\"bc1aeff\" data-element_type=\"column\">\n\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-wrap elementor-element-populated\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-840dc58 elementor-widget elementor-widget-heading\" data-id=\"840dc58\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"heading.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t<h2 class=\"elementor-heading-title elementor-size-default\">Medicare Help<\/h2>\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-6604a6b elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"6604a6b\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p>Medicare often leaves people confused with its complicated rules and a wide array of choices.<\/p><p>Watch the below <a href=\"https:\/\/flimp.live\/HubDeliverablesMedicare\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\"><strong>Medicare Eligibility video<\/strong><\/a> for helpful information.<\/p><p>If you are approaching Medicare eligibility, <strong>My Benefit Advisor<\/strong> can help you sort through the complexities and the tough decisions to find the solution that is right for you. Please view the flyer below for more information on available services and assistance.<\/p><p>If you have both Medicare and the BCBS group health plan and have questions on how benefits coordinate (i.e. which coverage pays first), please <strong>contact BCBS<\/strong> on the number on the back of your ID card.<\/p>\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-8b4f3ff elementor-widget elementor-widget-heading\" data-id=\"8b4f3ff\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"heading.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t<h2 class=\"elementor-heading-title elementor-size-default\">Additional Resources<\/h2>\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-9c12df9 elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"9c12df9\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<ul><li>Medicare benefits:<ul><li>Contact Medicare: 1-800-MEDICARE or <strong><a href=\"https:\/\/www.medicare.gov\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">medicare.gov<\/a><\/strong><\/li><li>Medicare publication \u2013<a href=\"https:\/\/www.medicare.gov\/publications\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\"><strong> Medicare &amp; You<\/strong><\/a><\/li><\/ul><\/li><li>Questions about enrolling in Medicare:<ul><li>Call Social Security at 1-800-772-1213 or visit socialsecurity.gov<\/li><\/ul><\/li><li>Contact a local State Health Insurance Assistance Program (SHIP):<ul><li>For free personalized counseling on Medicare coverage, claims, appeals, and help for people with limited income and resources. Call 1 800 MEDICARE or visit Medicare.gov\/contacts or visit shiptacenter.org to get the phone number of your local SHIP.<\/li><\/ul><\/li><li>Centers for Medicare &amp; Medicaid Services (CMS) resources:<ul><li><a href=\"https:\/\/www.cms.gov\/outreach-and-education\/find-your-provider-type\/employers-and-unions\/top-5-things-you-need-to-know-about-medicare-enrollment\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">5 things you need to know about signing up for Medicare<\/a><\/li><li><a href=\"https:\/\/www.cms.gov\/Outreach-and-Education\/Find-Your-Provider-Type\/Employers-and-Unions\/Web-resources-to-help-employees\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Web resources to help employees<\/a><\/li><li><a href=\"https:\/\/www.cms.gov\/Outreach-and-Education\/Find-Your-Provider-Type\/Employers-and-Unions\/Publications-to-share-with-employees\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Medicare publications to help employees<\/a><\/li><\/ul><\/li><\/ul>\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<\/section>\n\t\t\t\t<section class=\"elementor-section elementor-top-section elementor-element elementor-element-ecdd443 elementor-section-boxed elementor-section-height-default elementor-section-height-default\" data-id=\"ecdd443\" data-element_type=\"section\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-container elementor-column-gap-default\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-column elementor-col-50 elementor-top-column elementor-element elementor-element-aad95a4\" data-id=\"aad95a4\" data-element_type=\"column\">\n\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-wrap elementor-element-populated\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-bc80f2c elementor-widget elementor-widget-image\" data-id=\"bc80f2c\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"image.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<a href=\"https:\/\/flimp.live\/HubDeliverablesMedicare\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<img fetchpriority=\"high\" decoding=\"async\" wi